('54475','19251','5','Finca hotel in center of Mallorca to rent '),
('54476','19252','5','The capital Palma is about  20 minutes away driving. This neat property is located in the middle of a 30.000 m² plot. Its arquitecture maintains the traditional  mallorquin style,the interior is restored and allows modern guest-rooms, suits and a divine restaurant with a beautiful outside terrace. Embedded in the meditarranean garden there is a swimming pool with a couple of big sun terraces.\r\nThe hotel has 9 individually decorated suits and double bedrooms, 6 of them have their own terrace. Every room and suite has its own bathroom, aircondition and heater, Sat T-V, wifi, mini bar and safe. The bathrooms either have a shower or a whirl-pool-tub. The suits have different sized rooms and enough place for one or two extra guests. The tenant has built a little casita for himself with livingroom, kitchinette, bed room and bathroom.The restaurant brings the finest selected Mediterranean foods.\r\nRental conditions:                                                      Overtaking of the S.L.   The compensation  payment is  320.000€ + 21% IVA. \r\nmonthly rent:  from August 2014 is 4.500€                  from August 2015 is 5.000€                                       from 2016 is 5.500€ til the end of the lease no further ingrease.\r\nThe remaining term of the lease is 13 years. An option for three more years extension can be negociated.\r\nThe Real Estate comision is 1,5 times a monthly rent plus 5% of the traspaso plus 21% IVA, payable by the new tenant on the day of signing the contract.\r\nSince the hotel still is in progress, we can not deliver you any information nor pictures or address of the hotel. Please contact our office for further informations.'),
